---

---

<section class="process-section fade-up">
  <img
    src="/images/rupp-construction-team03.jpg"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="process-section__bg"
    loading="lazy"
  />

  <div class="container">
    <div class="speed-lines speed-lines--wide">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">HOW IT WORKS</h2>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-step__number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <h3 class="process-step__title">Free Quote</h3>
        <p class="process-step__desc">
          We walk the job, review the scope, and give you a detailed bid. No pressure, no surprises.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-step__number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <h3 class="process-step__title">Prep & Demo</h3>
        <p class="process-step__desc">
          Existing concrete removed and hauled. Ground graded and compacted. Rebar grid or wire mesh installed.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-step__number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <h3 class="process-step__title">The Pour</h3>
        <p class="process-step__desc">
          Concrete placed, screeded, and finished by an experienced crew. Forms stay until cured.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <span class="process-step__number" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <h3 class="process-step__title">Final Walkthrough</h3>
        <p class="process-step__desc">
          We review the finished work with you before calling it done. Any punch items addressed same week.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .process-section__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.08;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .process-section .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .process-step {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .process-step__number {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 64px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-border);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .process-step__title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .process-step__desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
